 With the death of Emperor <PERSON> Hirohito </PERSON> today and the ascension of Crown Prince <PERSON> Akihito </PERSON> to the Chrysanthemum Throne, here is the new order of heirs to the throne. 1. Crown Prince <PERSON> Naruhito </PERSON>, 28, formerly known as Prince <PERSON> Hiro </PERSON>, eldest son of <PERSON> Akihito </PERSON>. 2. <PERSON> Prince </PERSON> <PERSON> Aya </PERSON>, 23, second son of <PERSON> Akihito </PERSON>. 3. <PERSON> Prince </PERSON> <PERSON> Hitachi </PERSON>, 53, second son of <PERSON> Hirohito </PERSON>. 4. <PERSON> Prince </PERSON> <PERSON> Mikasa </PERSON>, 73, youngest brother of <PERSON> Hirohito </PERSON>. 5. Prince <PERSON> Tomohito </PERSON>, 42, eldest son of <LOCATION> Mikasa </LOCATION>. 6. <PERSON> Prince </PERSON> <PERSON> Katsura </PERSON>, 40, second son of <LOCATION> Mikasa </LOCATION>. 7. Prince <PERSON> Takamado </PERSON>, 34, third son of <LOCATION> Mikasa </LOCATION>.
