ories and factories in <LOCATION> America </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> Europe </LOCATION> and any spot of the world,'' <PERSON> Gadhafi </PERSON> concluded in his statement. On Friday, the <LOCATION> Libyan </LOCATION> government charged at a news conference and in official media that its planes were overwhelmed Wednesday by 14 `` hostile American aircraft.'' A government spokesman maintained the <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION> report that two <ORGANIZATION> Navy </ORGANIZATION> jets had acted in self-defense was `` a fabrication.'' <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION> provided the <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION> media with videotape taken by a <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION> aircraft of the encounter and showed photographs to the <ORGANIZATION> U.N. </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Security </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Council </ORGANIZATION> of what it said was a heavily armed Libyan plane involved in the encounter.
